#X text 438 202 LEGATO MODE - JUMP SMOOTHLY FROM ONE TO NEXT LED just
switch of the old leds (because each new led starts with clear message)
in order to do that we need a very large number send to the delay \,
witch will be overriten each time with a new clock bang;
#X text 438 270 CLOCK-SYNC MODE - all notes have the same length \,
can go from very short to max (master clock) We get value by multiplying
master clock * delFACTOR.;
#X text 439 319 RANDOM - take MASTERclock value \, divide it by 10
- this is the upper limit of random number generated with each bang
from master clock \, this value is then multiplied by LEDdelFACTOR
* 50;
